<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="zh-CN"><head><meta charSet="utf-8"/><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1, user-scalable=no"/><link rel="stylesheet" href="/_next/static/css/d92e24c3fc0c65cf.css" data-precedence="next"/><link rel="preload" as="script" fetchPriority="low" href="/_next/static/chunks/webpack-616e068a201ad621.js"/><script src="/_next/static/chunks/fd9d1056-b6edf2a6367e3325.js" async=""></script><script src="/_next/static/chunks/117-015bef3265851f8f.js" async=""></script><script src="/_next/static/chunks/main-app-bb43e700119fa1a3.js" async=""></script><script src="/_next/static/chunks/app/creator/video/page-309d171381d48830.js" async=""></script><title>AI短剧宇宙</title><meta name="description" content="人人都能创造AI连续剧宇宙"/><script src="/_next/static/chunks/polyfills-42372ed130431b0a.js" noModule=""></script></head><body class="min-h-screen bg-black text-white antialiased"><div class="min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-b from-zinc-950 to-black"><header class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-zinc-800 px-4 py-3"><button class="flex items-center gap-1 text-sm text-zinc-400 hover:text-white">← 返回</button><h1 class="text-sm font-semibold">🎬 视频生成</h1><div class="w-12"></div></header><div class="space-y-4 px-4 py-4"><div class="rounded-lg border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/50 p-3 text-xs leading-relaxed text-zinc-400"><p class="mb-1 font-medium text-zinc-300">🎬 创作流程</p><ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-1"><li>输入剧本 → AI 解析剧情结构</li><li>自动绑定角色库图片</li><li>生成分镜 + lock prompt</li><li>逐段生成视频片段</li><li>审核质量 → 输出成片</li></ol><p class="mt-2 text-yellow-400">💡 建议先创建角色，视频会自动匹配角色图</p></div><div><label class="mb-1.5 block text-xs font-medium text-zinc-400">输入剧本 <span class="text-zinc-600">（自然语言）</span></label><textarea placeholder="例如：煤球在酒吧喝咖啡突然遇到爆炸，被一道蓝光卷入时空裂缝，醒来发现被古代士兵包围" rows="4" class="w-full resize-none rounded-lg border border-zinc-700 bg-zinc-800 px-3 py-2.5 text-sm text-white placeholder-zinc-600 outline-none transition focus:border-blue-500"></textarea></div><div><p class="mb-1.5 text-[10px] text-zinc-600">试试示例：</p><div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2"><button class="rounded-lg border border-zinc-700 px-2.5 py-1.5 text-[10px] text-zinc-400 transition hover:border-zinc-500">示例 <!-- -->1</button><button class="rounded-lg border border-zinc-700 px-2.5 py-1.5 text-[10px] text-zinc-400 transition hover:border-zinc-500">示例 <!-- -->2</button><button class="rounded-lg border border-zinc-700 px-2.5 py-1.5 text-[10px] text-zinc-400 transition hover:border-zinc-500">示例 <!-- -->3</button></div></div><div><label class="mb-1.5 block text-xs font-medium text-zinc-400">视频风格</label><div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2"><button class="rounded-lg border px-3 py-1.5 text-xs transition border-blue-500 bg-blue-500/20 text-blue-400">🎯 自动识别</button><button class="rounded-lg border px-3 py-1.5 text-xs transition border-zinc-700 text-zinc-400 hover:border-zinc-500">🏯 古装</button><button class="rounded-lg border px-3 py-1.5 text-xs transition border-zinc-700 text-zinc-400 hover:border-zinc-500">🏙️ 现代</button><button class="rounded-lg border px-3 py-1.5 text-xs transition border-zinc-700 text-zinc-400 hover:border-zinc-500">🗡️ 仙侠</button><button class="rounded-lg border px-3 py-1.5 text-xs transition border-zinc-700 text-zinc-400 hover:border-zinc-500">🚀 科幻</button><button class="rounded-lg border px-3 py-1.5 text-xs transition border-zinc-700 text-zinc-400 hover:border-zinc-500">🔍 悬疑</button><button class="rounded-lg border px-3 py-1.5 text-xs transition border-zinc-700 text-zinc-400 hover:border-zinc-500">💕 甜宠</button><button class="rounded-lg border px-3 py-1.5 text-xs transition border-zinc-700 text-zinc-400 hover:border-zinc-500">⏳ 穿越</button></div></div><button disabled="" class="w-full rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-purple-600 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:from-blue-400 hover:to-purple-500 disabled:opacity-50">🎬 生成视频</button></div></div><script src="/_next/static/chun